com.sun.darkstar.example.snowman.game.task
Class Task

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.darkstar.example.snowman.game.task.Task
All Implemented Interfaces:
ITask
Direct Known Subclasses:
CreateSnowballTask, RealTimeTask
public abstract class Task
extends Object
implements ITask

Task defines the most basic abstraction of all types of tasks. Each Task has an unique pair of ETaskType and ETask enumeration defined at construction time.

Task also maintains a reference to Game in order to allow subclasses to access game data for logic execution.

Subclasses of Task needs to implement execution logic details.
